+ The Solar_Controller_Front Class

++ Inheritance

* [Solar_Base::HomePage Solar_Base]

 * Solar_Controller_Front

Front-controller class for Solar.

An example front-controller "index.php" for your web root:

<code type="php">
require 'Solar.php';
Solar::start();
$front = Solar::factory('Solar_Controller_Front');
$front->display();
Solar::stop();
</code>